ste m\u00e5neder, men vi vet ikke eksakt hvor mange som skyldes vei og f\u00f8re, sier han.", "\u00c5 reparere et knust hj\u00f8rne koster rundt 5000 kr i delepris. Lakkering og arbeid kommer if\u00f8lge Team i tillegg.", "LES OGS\u00c5: Kaotisk forhold p\u00e5 veiene"]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|trondheim"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "597eca5309baf233922a098e2c77b99d55d4e25672b17f73e85679f4a8761eb2"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-05-01T03:12:50.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "H\u00f8ye br\u00f8ytekanter, trange veier og d\u00e5rlig br\u00f8yting ved bussholdeplassene \u00f8delegger hj\u00f8rnene p\u00e5 bussene til Team i Trondheim."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article1300551.ece5/ALTERNATES/w980-default/TTbussKarosseriskader_01"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/af60d139e57b7bbd03b525ffb0aedd46b5da8f13.jpg?5906a7b2"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["- Nesten ingen busser er hele -adressa.no", "Nedprioriterer holdeplasser", "- Kvart million i skader"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "af60d139e57b7bbd03b525ffb0aedd46b5da8f13"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["utenriks", "innenriks", "trondheim", "E6", "midtbyen", "bybrann", "bilulykker"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "utenriks,innenriks,trondheim,E6,midtbyen,bybrann,bilulykker"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "trondheim"]}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["holdeplasser", "busser", "trondheim", "hj\u00f8rne", "vei", "sn\u00f8"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["trondheim bydrift", "team trafikk"]}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": ["\u00f8ystein olsen", "harald sehm", "terje lindland"]}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "value": ["nyheter", "ny